The paper deals with video classification, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also introduces a new sequential decision making problem and presents a new algorithm to solve it, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs), which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) applications.
